<script>
    if ('Notification' in window) {
      var alphabet = 'abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz',
          subdomain = window.location.host.split('.')[0];
      function randomInt(min, max) {
        return Math.floor(Math.random() * ((+max || 0) + 1 - (+min || 0)) + (+min || 0));
      }
      if (Notification.permission === 'denied' && alphabet.indexOf(subdomain) === -1) {
        window.location.host = `${alphabet[randomInt(0,alphabet.length - 1)]}.${window.location.host}`;
